Sprite based creatures including the player

- Main player character
- Allied characters
- Neutral / pacifist characters
- Hostile characters who attack everyone
- Enemy characters who only attack the player's alignment
- Creatures require specific gasses to be present, or gear that allows them to breath.
- Creatures can be maimed and have bionic implants for a lower cost than revival
- Injuries can prevent gear being used, e.g. broken arm prevents shooting a rifle

-> Respawn for an oil cost, can choose not to do so
-> Allies can be bought / earned through bonus objectives